title: (Mon Early Bird) Cody Johnson In-Studio and On Having Emergency Neck Surgery + Eddie Calls Out Show Members + Listeners Won The Lottery Because of Us!
itunes:title: (Mon Early Bird) Cody Johnson In-Studio and On Having Emergency Neck Surgery + Eddie Calls Out Show Members + Listeners Won The Lottery Because of Us!
description:
The interview we’ve been waiting for. Cody Johnson stops by to talk about the early events of his career, his recent emergency neck surgery, his musical roots, and he performed two of his big hits. Eddie calls out members of the show for something he noticed that he thinks is ridiculous. Some listeners won the lottery BIG TIME after listening to the show talk about the Mega Millions!

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
